Datenquelle: E-Control

Data source
-----------
E-Control Ladestellenverzeichnis API (e-charging.e-control.at)

Required attribution string
---------------------------
This integration emits the following attribution on every sensor and
binary_sensor (via the `attribution` state attribute) and in every
diagnostics download:

    Datenquelle: E-Control

If you build a Lovelace card or any other user-facing UI on top of this
integration, please keep this attribution visible. The contractual
attribution string is defined as a single source of truth in
`custom_components/ladestellen_austria/const.py` (`ATTRIBUTION`) and
imported by `sensor.py` and `binary_sensor.py`.

